OL,3,CJersey man sentenced for carrying out
OL,4,Cillegal gas work in the UK
OL,6,FAn investigation by Britain's national
OL,7,Fregulator for workplace health and
OL,8,Fsafety, Health and Safety Executive
OL,9,F(HSC), found multiple failings by Owen
OL,10,Fand that he was not registered to
OL,11,Fundertake any form of gas work since
OL,12,FWednesday, 20 October 2021.
OL,14,FHSE inspector, Simon Jones, said: "The
OL,15,Fwork that he undertook was found to be
OL,16,Fdangerous, putting the lives of the
OL,17,Fhomeowners and their four young
OL,18,Fchildren at risk."
