OL,3,CJersey man sentenced for carrying out
OL,4,Cillegal gas work in the UK
OL,6,FThe court heard that Owen attended a
OL,7,Fproperty on Barton Hill, Torquay, in
OL,8,FFebruary 2023, where he removed an old
OL,9,Fboiler and installed a new one.
OL,11,FHowever, the homeowners found the
OL,12,Fboiler did not work properly and said
OL,13,FOwen was dismissive of their concerns.
OL,15,FThe homeowners then arranged for
OL,16,Fanother company to check the
OL,17,Finstallation, where the plumber said
OL,18,Fthey had "serious concerns" and called
OL,19,Fthe emergency gas provider.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
