OL,3,CJersey man sentenced for carrying out
OL,4,Cillegal gas work in the UK
OL,6,FThe situation was then classified as
OL,7,F"immediately dangerous" by the
OL,8,Femergency provider after it found a
OL,9,Fgas leak on the supply pipe, and
OL,10,Ftherefore, the provider capped the
OL,11,Fsupply.
OL,13,FThe Gas Safe Register, the official
OL,14,Fgas registration body, was later
OL,15,Fcalled to the home, where they also
OL,16,Ffound further defects in the gas
OL,17,Fboiler installation.
