OL,3,CJersey man sentenced for carrying out
OL,4,Cillegal gas work in the UK
OL,6,FA third company was hired by the
OL,7,Fhomeowners to rectify the faults,
OL,8,Fwhich uncovered further issues created
OL,9,Fby Owen.
OL,11,FAn investigation by the HSE found Owen
OL,12,Fwas not registered with the Gas Safe
OL,13,FRegister, which is a legal requirement.
OL,15,FIt added that Owen had not been
OL,16,Fregistered since Wednesday, 20 October
OL,17,F2021, when his registration had lapsed.
