OL,3,CJersey man sentenced for carrying out
OL,4,Cillegal gas work in the UK
OL,6,FA statement from the HSE said:
OL,7,F"Carrying out gas work without
OL,8,Fregistration is illegal and
OL,9,Fpotentially dangerous, as unqualified
OL,10,Fwork can lead to gas leaks, fires,
OL,11,Fexplosions, and carbon monoxide
OL,12,Fpoisoning."
OL,14,FOwen pleaded not guilty at Exeter
OL,15,FCrown Court to contravening Sections
OL,16,F3(3), 26(1) and 27(1) of the Gas
OL,17,FSafety (Installation and Use)
OL,18,FRegulations 1998.
