OL,3,CJersey man sentenced for carrying out
OL,4,Cillegal gas work in the UK
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to 15 months in
OL,7,Fprison, suspended for 18 months,
OL,8,Fordered to undertake 150 hours of
OL,9,Funpaid work and to pay costs of #1,000
OL,10,Fby the court on Wednesday, 7 January.
OL,12,FHealth and Safety Executive inspector,
OL,13,FSimon Jones, said: "Ben Owen undertook
OL,14,Fgas work which he knew he was not
OL,15,Fregistered to do, and the work that he
OL,16,Fundertook was found to be dangerous,
OL,17,Fputting the lives of the homeowners
OL,18,Fand their four young children at risk.
