OL,6,F"All gas work must be conducted by
OL,7,Fregistered Gas Safe engineers to
OL,8,Fensure the highest standards are met
OL,9,Fto prevent injury and loss of life.
OL,11,F"We advise all householders to check
OL,12,Fthat anyone they allow to work on
OL,13,Ftheir gas supply is Gas Safe
OL,14,Fregistered. This can be done at the
OL,15,FGas Safe Register website."
